{"id":1698652,"retrievedAt":"2026-05-20T13:57:32.659Z","response":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[{"id":99,"name":"Documentary"}],"homepage":"","id":1698652,"imdb_id":null,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_title":"When I See Them, I See Us","overview":"We choose to build with one another in a shoulder to shoulder struggle against state-sanctioned violence. A violence that is manifest in the speed of bullets and batons and tear gas that pierce our bodies. One that is latent in the edifice of law and concrete that work together to, physically and figuratively, cage us. We choose to join one another in resistance not because our struggles are the same but because we each struggle against the formidable forces of structural racism and the carceral and lethal technologies deployed to maintain them. This video intends to interrupt that process – to assert our humanity – and to stand together in an affirmation of life and a commitment to resistance. From Ferguson to Gaza, from Baltimore to Jerusalem, from Charleston to Bethlehem, we will be free.","popularity":0.0071,"poster_path":"/ry5A4hkjDFXYYpS5jk7IytVIfuE.jpg","production_companies":[{"id":299040,"logo_path":null,"name":"Jewish Voice for Peace","origin_country":""},{"id":299041,"logo_path":null,"name":"The Dream Defenders","origin_country":""},{"id":299042,"logo_path":null,"name":"Street Art United States","origin_country":""},{"id":299043,"logo_path":null,"name":"BYP 100","origin_country":""},{"id":299044,"logo_path":null,"name":"DC Palestinian Film and Arts Festival","origin_country":""},{"id":299045,"logo_path":null,"name":"Institute for Middle East Understanding","origin_country":""},{"id":299046,"logo_path":null,"name":"Quilting Point Productions","origin_country":""}],"production_countries":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","name":"United States of America"}],"release_date":"2021-03-08","revenue":0,"runtime":3,"softcore":false,"spoken_languages":[{